data.name: checkBoxRestorePrompt.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, a prompt in the bottom right hand corner appears for a short time at startup. This prompt asks to restore the last session. For perfomance, keep this option unchecked

data.name: checkBoxAddTabOnStart.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, adds a blank tab to the tab control when the program starts

data.name: checkBoxSingleInstance.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, the program will only allow on instance of itself to be open. Meaning documents will be loaded into separate tabs in opposed to separate program instances. (Restart needed for change to take effect)

data.name: numberBoxVertPadding.ToolTip
data.value: The top and bottom padding of the reading text

data.name: numberBoxHorizPadding.ToolTip
data.value: The left and right padding of the text area

data.name: checkBoxReadingTopmost.ToolTip
data.value: Keeps the reading view on top of other windows

data.name: numberBoxReadingWidth.ToolTip
data.value: The width of the text area in pixels

data.name: checkBoxAddTitle.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, adds the document title at the top of the print outs

data.name: numberBoxMaxRecents.ToolTip
data.value: The maximum amount of recent files to list

data.name: checkBoxSelectionMargin.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, shows the selection margin in the text area

data.name: checkBoxMultilineTabs.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, tabs will not overflow out of view

data.name: checkBoxTrackSelection.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, the selected text in the plaintext box will be tracked with by two green rectangles. The rectangles appear on the left and top of the plaintext box

data.name: checkBoxAutoWordSelection.ToolTip
data.value: When checked, entire words will automatically be selected when selecting characters within the said word

data.name: textBoxSigInsert.ToolTip
data.value: The text that will be inserted at the end of the document when inserting signature
